metadata.name: Galactic Apostles
metadata.description:
What began as a vision, led to the creation of an image that is totally unique and breaks the boundaries of what has been done before.

One of Australia's most recognisable natural landmarks has been portrayed in a completely new light through the creation of this image.

The milky way core rising above the remnants of the 12 apostles symbolises the significance of the universe and how each day brings new meaning and hope to this world.

The 12 Apostles, Victoria, Australia.
